<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Find Your Daddy - Sur Demande</title>
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .header {
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url('https://lannetech.com/client/admin/img/674f28c388f3d.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 400px;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .search-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
        }

        .search-box {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #e27730;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .tags {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tag {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .feature {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .testimonial {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border: solid 1px rgb(200, 200, 200);
        }

        .testimonial-content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .testimonial-image {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .stars {
            color: #e27730;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="search-container">
          <div class="logo">
              <img width="100" src="https://lannetech.com/client/admin/img/674f2a533026b.png" class="logo-icon">
              <h1>Find Your Daddy.<br>Sur Demande.</h1>
          </div>
          <p>Professional courses, led by the world’s top Daddy.</p>
            <div class="search-box">
                <input type="text" placeholder="What kind off Daddy you need ?">
                <button class="btn">Search</button>
                <button class="btn">View All Daddy</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tags">
                <span class="tag">Popular:</span>
                <span class="tag">Informaticien</span>
                <span class="tag">Mécano</span>
                <span class="tag">Plombier</span>
                <span class="tag">Maçon</span>
                <span class="tag">Barbecue</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h3><i class='bx bxs-objects-vertical-bottom'></i> Practical skills</h3>
            <p>Trouver les daddy qui ont le skill dont tu as besoin</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3><i class='bx bx-dumbbell' ></i> Find the best Daddy</h3>
            <p>Trouvez le meilleur Darons sur la platforme #1 des aides à la personne!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3><i class='bx bx-money-withdraw' ></i> No subscription fees</h3>
            <p>Pas d'abonnement, payer les daddy directement vos tâches via le site</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
        <div class="testimonial-content">
            <p>"Marcus did an amazing job cooking for our mama, she almost got cooked!"</p>
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p>Jean - Noel Toushuss</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-image">
            <h3>Marcus Spencer</h3>
            <p>Cooking Master,<br>Meat Lover and expert in flams.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
